{#- LLM-facing text is English-only: Cyrillic uses roughly 2–3× more tokens per word.
    This Jinja comment is stripped and never sent to the model.
    State summary for enrich_fast <response-state> MIME part.
    Variables: is_empty (bool), live_count (int), total_chars (int),
              chunks (list of {position: int, content: str|None, deleted: bool}). -#}
{% if is_empty -%}
Response buffer is empty.
{%- else -%}
Response buffer ({{ live_count }} chunks, ~{{ total_chars }} chars):
{% for chunk in chunks -%}
{% if chunk.deleted -%}
[{{ chunk.position }}] [DELETED]
{%- else -%}
[{{ chunk.position }}] {{ chunk.content | replace("\n", " ") }}
{%- endif %}
{% endfor -%}
{%- endif %}
